Description_lang: Critical strike chance increased by $s1%. Critical strike damage bonus of your attacks that generate combo points increased by $s2%.

description_blz.en_US: Critical strike chance increased by 1%. Critical strike damage bonus of your attacks that generate combo points increased by 10%.
description_blz.es_MX: La probabilidad de golpe crítico aumenta un 1%. La bonificación de probabilidad de golpe crítico de tus ataques que generan p. de combo aumenta un 10%.
description_blz.pt_BR: Chance de acerto crítico aumentada em 1%. Bônus de dano de acerto crítico dos seus ataques que geram pontos de combo aumentado em 10%.
description_blz.de_DE: Erhöht die kritische Trefferchance um 1%. Der kritische Schadensbonus Eurer Angriffe, die Combopunkte erzeugen, ist um 10% erhöht.
description_blz.en_GB: Critical strike chance increased by 1%. Critical strike damage bonus of your attacks that generate combo points increased by 10%.
description_blz.es_ES: Probabilidad de golpe crítico aumentada un 1%. Bonus de daño crítico de los ataques que generan puntos de combo aumentado un 10%.
description_blz.fr_FR: Les chances de coup critique sont augmentées de 1%. Le bonus aux dégâts critiques de vos attaques générant des points de combo est augmenté de 10%.
description_blz.it_IT: Aumenta la probabilità di critico del 1%. Aumenta il bonus dei danni critici inflitti dagli attacchi che forniscono punti combo del 10%.
description_blz.ru_RU: Вероятность критического удара повышена на 1%. Увеличивает бонус к критическому урону от ваших атак, продлевающих длину серии приемов, на 10%.
description_blz.ko_KR: 치명타 및 극대화율이 1%만큼 증가합니다. 연계 점수를 생성하는 공격의 치명타 및 극대화 피해가 10%만큼 증가합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 造成致命一擊的機率提高1%。產生連擊點數的攻擊致命一擊傷害加成提高10%。
description_blz.zh_CN: 爆击几率提高1%。生成连击点数的攻击的爆击伤害提高10%。
